# 能力分估计（因子得分）


::: {#fig-cor-fact-scores-among-selection .cell .column-page}

```{.r .cell-code}
tar_load(scores_factor, store = projects$confirm_factors$store)
factors <- c("g", dimensions$dim_label)
for (factor in factors) {
  p <- scores_factor |>
    filter(theory == "bf") |>
    pivot_wider(
      id_cols = user_id,
      names_from = name,
      values_from = all_of(factor)
    ) |>
    select(!user_id) |>
    GGally::ggpairs() +
    ggtitle(factor)
  print(p)
}
```

